<br>
I expect a lot of these types of changes down the road, including changes to but not limited to: PBT stacking, Pet LOS abuse, Stealth &amp; one shotting. Don't be surprised if these abilities change eventually. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6B8E23><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/bforgottentruthforeignlegion.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=lunasea>lunasea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(5/1/02 4:22:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1092.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 1.50c heheheehehehehehehehehehe</span><hr size=1> my 2 cents:<br>
Sorc's are all about CC just like tanks are all about melee and wizards all about DD.  Anytime you mess with the primary purpose of a class you better tread with caution.  Is the current Mez situation a problem? I think so.  Do tanks need something more in RvR?  Absolutely.<br>
<br>
