<br>
1) Shorten the range of mez.  Possibly 1000 feet.  This is WELL within reach of every caster.  It forces mez for use in closer combat.  Tanks would have ample opportunity to spot an incoming mezzer and take action.  It also preserves tactics with mez.  A group of all tanks and 1 cleric is not a well balanced group.  IMO a group that includes a mezer SHOULD be able to annihilate such a poorly balanced group.<br>
<br>
2) Increase ability to resist mez specifically.  Be VERY careful with this one.  There should NEVER be a situation where a class or person can always or even over 50% of the time be able to resist mez.  This makes a player make choices: do I use this +12 str item or the +12% mez resistance item?<br>
