3) Reduce the effectiveness of cleric mez.  If you want to mez take a sorcerer.  A cleric is either a healer, a buffer, or a pious warrior.  IMO cleric mez is vastly overpowered.  Although they have to get up close they have the HP and AF to take the hits and the spell is an insta.  If cleric's should even have the spell I say nerf the hell out of it: 25% effective.<br>
<br>
I believe the effect of those changes would prevent sorc's from mezing from afar, reward those groups that have better class balance, AND preserve most of the effectiveness of a mezer.<br>
